        "content": "4. Get Thread History\nFor reply emails, this node fetches the full Gmail thread using the thread ID. This allows the system to understand previous conversation context instead of analyzing only the latest message.\n\n5. Process Thread History\nThis code node processes the Gmail thread history. It extracts clean email addresses and removes quoted replies or signatures from message snippets, ensuring only meaningful customer messages are analyzed.\n\n6. Aggregate\nThis node combines all processed messages from the thread into a single array. The aggregated conversation is stored as extracted_data, which is later passed to AI models as conversation context.",
