    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "10. Edit Fields1\nThis node passes cleaned email data forward while preserving all existing fields. It prepares the data structure for the main AI support analysis.\n\n11. AI Analysis Agent\nThis is the main AI support agent. It analyzes the customer message and conversation history, categorizes the issue, assigns priority, decides if human escalation is required, and generates a professional reply. It can also query the Qdrant knowledge base for accurate answers.\n\n12. Qdrant Vector Store\nThis node retrieves relevant knowledge base documents using embeddings. It provides contextual information to the AI Analysis Agent so responses are accurate and consistent.\n\n13. Groq Chat Model\nThis node provides the language model used by the AI Analysis Agent to generate structured responses efficiently.\n",
