    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "14. Process AI Analysis\nThis node extracts structured fields from the AI agent response such as category, priority, reasoning, escalation flag, AI response text, and SLA hours based on priority.\n\n15. Edit Fields\nThis node calculates the ticket due date using SLA hours and appends it to the data while keeping all other fields unchanged.\n\n16. Needs Escalation?\nThis IF node checks whether the ticket requires human escalation. If escalation is needed, it follows the human-review path; otherwise, it continues with auto-resolution.\n\n",
