    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "17. Needs Human Review Label\nThis node applies a Gmail label indicating that the ticket needs human review. This helps support agents quickly identify unresolved issues.\n\n18. Send Automated Reply\nThis node sends the AI-generated reply email to the customer automatically when escalation is not required.\n\n19. Auto Resolved Label\nThis node applies a Gmail label indicating the issue was automatically resolved by the AI system.\n\n20. Log Ticket to Google Sheets\nThis node logs the full ticket information into Google Sheets, including ticket ID, customer details, AI response, escalation status, SLA, timestamp, and original message.\n\n21. Send Status Update\nThis node sends a real-time notification to Telegram containing ticket status, priority, category, and resolution state for admin monitoring.\n",
